https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/move-to-south-africa-with-20-highest-paying-jobs\/#14_Chief_Audit_Officer\" title=\"14. Chief Audit Officer\">14. Chief Audit Officer<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/move-to-south-africa-with-20-highest-paying-jobs\/#15_HR_DirectorExecutive\" title=\"15. HR Director\/Executive\">15. HR Director\/Executive<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/move-to-south-africa-with-20-highest-paying-jobs\/#16_Country_Manager\" title=\"16. Country Manager\">16. Country Manager<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/move-to-south-africa-with-20-highest-paying-jobs\/#17_IT_Director\" title=\"17. IT Director\">17. IT Director<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-18\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/move-to-south-africa-with-20-highest-paying-jobs\/#18_Chief_Enterprise_Architect\" title=\"18. Chief Enterprise Architect\">18. Chief Enterprise Architect<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-19\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/move-to-south-africa-with-20-highest-paying-jobs\/#19_Head_of_Sales\" title=\"19. Head of Sales\">19. Head of Sales<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-20\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/move-to-south-africa-with-20-highest-paying-jobs\/#20_Private_EquityCorporate_Finance\" title=\"20. Private Equity\/Corporate Finance\">20. Private Equity\/Corporate Finance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-21\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/move-to-south-africa-with-20-highest-paying-jobs\/#21_Head_of_Software_Development\" title=\"21. Head of Software Development\">21. Head of Software Development<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<h2 id=\"1-group-regional-cfo\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_GroupRegional_CFO\"><\/span><strong>1. Group\/Regional CFO<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This particular group in the Finance and Accounting sector earns R3.0 million \u2013 R5.0 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"2-vp-of-supply-chain\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_VP_of_supply_chain\"><\/span><span id=\"2_VP_of_supply_chain\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>2. VP of supply chain<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This group of people in the supply chain &amp;amp; logistics sector earns an estimated income of R2.5 million \u2013 R3.9 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"3-finance-director\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Finance_Director\"><\/span><span id=\"3_Finance_Director\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>3. Finance Director<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Finance Director in the Finance and Accounting sector earns a rough estimate of about R2.0 million \u2013 R3.5 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"4-chief-information-officer\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Chief_Information_Officer\"><\/span><span id=\"4_Chief_Information_Officer\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>4. Chief Information Officer<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Chief Information Officer in the technology sector earns R1.6 million \u2013 R3.0 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"5-chief-marketing-officer\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Chief_Marketing_Officer\"><\/span><span id=\"5_Chief_Marketing_Officer\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>5. Chief Marketing Officer<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Sales\/Marketing Industry CMO earns R2.0 million \u2013 R3.0 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"6-general-manager\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_General_Manager\"><\/span><span id=\"6_General_Manager\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>6. General Manager<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Sales Marketing Industry General Manager earns an estimated R1.8 million \u2013 R2.8 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"7-vp-of-procurement\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7_VP_of_Procurement\"><\/span><span id=\"7_VP_of_Procurement\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>7. VP of Procurement<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The VP of Procurement earns an estimated R1.8 million \u2013 R2.8 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"8-supply-chain-logistics-director\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"8_Supply_ChainLogistics_Director\"><\/span><span id=\"8_Supply_ChainLogistics_Director\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>8. Supply Chain\/Logistics Director<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The supply chain Director earns R1.7 million \u2013 R2.9 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"9-group-tax-director\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"9_Group_Tax_Director\"><\/span><span id=\"9_Group_Tax_Director\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>9. Group Tax Director<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Group Tax Director in the Finance and Accounting sector earns R2.2 million \u2013 R2.7 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"10-project-director\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"10_Project_Director\"><\/span><span id=\"10_Project_Director\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>10. Project Director<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The project director in the engineering and manufacturing industry earns a rough estimate of R1.6 million to R2.2 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"11-chief-technology-officer\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"11_Chief_Technology_Officer\"><\/span><span id=\"11_Chief_Technology_Officer\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>11. Chief Technology Officer<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The CTO in the Technology sector earns about R1.4 million \u2013 R2.1 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"12-manufacturing-director\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"12_Manufacturing_Director\"><\/span><span id=\"12_Manufacturing_Director\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>12. Manufacturing Director<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Manufacturing Director in the Manufacturing Industry earns R1.5 million \u2013 R2.3 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"13-vp-of-sales\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"13_VP_of_Sales\"><\/span><span id=\"13_VP_of_Sales\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>13. VP of Sales\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The VP of Sales in the Sales\/Marketing Industry earns R2.0 million \u2013 R2.8 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"14-chief-audit-officer\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"14_Chief_Audit_Officer\"><\/span><span id=\"14_Chief_Audit_Officer\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>14. Chief Audit Officer<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Chief Audit Officer in the Finance and Accounting sector earns R1.6 million \u2013 R2.4 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"15-hr-director-executive\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"15_HR_DirectorExecutive\"><\/span><span id=\"15_HR_DirectorExecutive\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>15. HR Director\/Executive<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The HR Director\/Executive in the human resource department earns about R1.8 million \u2013 R3.2 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"16-country-manager\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"16_Country_Manager\"><\/span><span id=\"16_Country_Manager\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>16. Country Manager<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Country Manager in the Sales\/Marketing Industry earns a rough estimate of about R1.8 million \u2013 R2.6 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"17-it-director\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"17_IT_Director\"><\/span><span id=\"17_IT_Director\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>17. IT Director<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The IT Director earns R1.3 million \u2013 R2.0 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"18-chief-enterprise-architect\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"18_Chief_Enterprise_Architect\"><\/span><span id=\"18_Chief_Enterprise_Architect\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>18. Chief Enterprise Architect<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Chief Enterprise Architect earns about R1.5 million \u2013 R2.0 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"19-head-of-sales\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"19_Head_of_Sales\"><\/span><span id=\"19_Head_of_Sales\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>19. Head of Sales<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Head of Sales earns about R1.6 million \u2013 R2.0 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"20-private-equity-corporate-finance\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"20_Private_EquityCorporate_Finance\"><\/span><span id=\"20_Private_EquityCorporate_Finance\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>20. Private Equity\/Corporate Finance<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This group of persons in Banking &amp; Finance earns about R1.5 million \u2013 R2.0 million yearly.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"21-head-of-software-development\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"21_Head_of_Software_Development\"><\/span><span id=\"21_Head_of_Software_Development\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>21. Head of Software Development<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This group earns a rough estimate of about R1.1 million \u2013 R2.0 million yearly.<\/p>\n<p>This list was compiled in no particular order. These jobs are a few of the highest-paying jobs in South Africa.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"When it comes to lucrative job opportunities in South Africa, a range of professions offer high salaries. While&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":14787,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14785"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14785"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14785\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/14787"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14785"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=14785"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=14785"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}